parameters.name: init Optional
parameters.description: An options object containing any custom settings that you want to apply to the event object. Options are as follows: tag: A developer-defined unique identifier for this SyncEvent. lastChance: A Boolean indicating that the user agent will not make further synchronization attempts after the current attempt.

members.name: SyncEvent.tag
members.description: Returns the developer-defined identifier for this SyncEvent.

members.name: SyncEvent.lastChance
members.description: Returns true if the user agent will not make further synchronization attempts after the current attempt.
